  <entry>
    <title>美化博客</title>
    <url>/2024/07/20/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>Hexo博客NexT主题下添加分类、标签、关于菜单项<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/mqdxiaoxiao/article/details/93644533">https://blog.csdn.net/mqdxiaoxiao/article/details/93644533</a></p>
<p>隐藏页脚的 “由 xxxx 强力驱动”<br>修改主题配置文件 footer 部分的 powered 的值为你想要的<br>footer:</p>
<h1 id="隐藏-footer-‘由-HEXO-强力驱动’"><a href="#隐藏-footer-‘由-HEXO-强力驱动’" class="headerlink" title="隐藏 footer ‘由 HEXO 强力驱动’"></a>隐藏 footer ‘由 HEXO 强力驱动’</h1><p>  powered: false # false: 不显示 true: 显示</p>
<p>更改主题配置文件</p>
<p>cd 博客目录<br>vim themes&#x2F;next&#x2F;_config.yml<br>找到下面这行，取消注释即可。</p>
<h1 id="Sidebar-Avatar"><a href="#Sidebar-Avatar" class="headerlink" title="Sidebar Avatar"></a>Sidebar Avatar</h1><h1 id="in-theme-directory-source-images-images-avatar-gif"><a href="#in-theme-directory-source-images-images-avatar-gif" class="headerlink" title="in theme directory(source&#x2F;images): &#x2F;images&#x2F;avatar.gif"></a>in theme directory(source&#x2F;images): &#x2F;images&#x2F;avatar.gif</h1><h1 id="in-site-directory-source-uploads-uploads-avatar-gif"><a href="#in-site-directory-source-uploads-uploads-avatar-gif" class="headerlink" title="in site  directory(source&#x2F;uploads): &#x2F;uploads&#x2F;avatar.gif"></a>in site  directory(source&#x2F;uploads): &#x2F;uploads&#x2F;avatar.gif</h1><p>avatar: &#x2F;images&#x2F;avatar_2.gif<br>上传自定义的图片到下列目录：</p>
<p>博客目录&#x2F;themes&#x2F;next&#x2F;source&#x2F;images&#x2F;</p>
<p>然后在上面的主题配置文件中更改相应路径即可。</p>
]]></content>
